    <description>Stems 2–11 dm, glabrous throughout. Cauline leaves: blade conduplicate distally,
        margins entire, surfaces glabrous. Racemes not secund; rachis flexuous. Fruiting pedicels
        10–32 mm, glabrous. Flowers: sepals dark purple-black, 7–8 mm, glabrous; petals dark purple,
        10–12 mm; adaxial filaments 8–10 mm. Fruits divaricate-ascending, straight; valves glabrous.
        2n = 28.</description>
